title: Living Your Passion Isn't Rainbows and Unicorns, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO43
description: Live your passion.  That's what Andy Frisella says.  But don't make the huge mistake of thinking that means life will be easy.  Life wasn't meant to be easy.  You're not meant to be a wilting flower. You are called to be tough-minded, battle-tested, and made better through struggle.
